items.question:
Has the entity disclosed the following for each class of provision (comparative information not required) [2]:
  a) the carrying amount at the beginning and end of the period [2];
  b) additional provisions made in the period, including increases to existing provisions [2];
  c) amounts used (i.e., incurred and charged against the provision) during the period [2];
  d) unused amounts reversed during the period [2]; and
  e) the increase during the period in the discounted amount arising from the passage of time and the effect of any change in the discount rate [2]?
